| $β_{dist}$ (Convergence) | 0.348 | 0.015 | 23.164 | 0.000 |
| $β_{inter\_trade}$ | 0.022 | 0.013 | 1.737 | 0.082 |
| $β_{inter\_gov}$ | 0.016 | 0.015 | 1.061 | 0.289 |

